	  <h1>Classic Drawing &  Figure Painting <h1><h2> by Ruth Block</h2>
	  <h5>Class from
June 26 to June 29, 2011</h5>
	  <p>Special High intensity 4 day anatomy and drawing class with the renown Ruth Block. Her DVD's and videos have been a staple of home learning for almost two decades. She is the head of department and lead drawing instructor at The Art Institute of California. For professionals who want quick improvement of their representation of human anatomy as well as amateurs who want to start out on the right foot.</p> 
<p>Please see Ruth's description on this website as well as her website. We are thrilled to have her as this class is being squeezed into her busy teaching and exhibition schedule. This will be the least expensive class offered with Ruth Block by Hawaiian Art Journey this year.</p> 
<p><strong>The price for this class is $1687, all inclusive for a double occupency hale, or $2188 for a single hale.</strong> Please call 510-808-4424 to register for this class.</p>	  <hr width="90%" size="1" />
